== Summary ==
New Zealand is located in the Southwest Pacific Ocean. It is an island country in the southwestern part of Polynesia, with the Pacific Ocean stretching indefinitely to its north, east, and south. The Tasman Sea, a marginal sea of the South Pacific, lies to its west, separating it from Australia. It was the primary filming location for [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]], [[The Hobbit (film series)|''The Hobbit'' (film series)]] and the first season of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]''.

== Information about New Zealand ==

==== Government ====
New Zealand is a constitutional monarchy with a parliamentary system of government. This means its head of state and head of government are separate and have different roles.
